    "title": "Career Opportunity Production Engineer at SAIL International Enterprises",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at SAIL International Enterprises. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Production Engineer to strengthen our Bhopal-based team.\n\nAbout SAIL International Enterprises:\nSAIL International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in 5S\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SAIL International Enterprises!",
